&amp;lt;h2 id=&amp;quot;usage-guidelines&amp;quot; tabindex=&amp;quot;-1&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Usage Guidelines &amp;lt;a class=&amp;quot;anchor&amp;quot; href=&amp;quot;#usage-guidelines&amp;quot; aria-hidden=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;&amp;gt;#&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;When working with navigation components, consider the following best practices:&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;ul&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Provide clear visual indicators for the current location&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Use consistent navigation patterns throughout your application&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Ensure navigation is accessible via keyboard and screen readers&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Adapt navigation components for different screen sizes&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Use appropriate icons and labels to improve clarity&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Keep navigation structure simple and intuitive&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;For component-specific guidelines, refer to the individual component documentation pages.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;

&amp;lt;h1 id=&amp;quot;feedback-components&amp;quot; tabindex=&amp;quot;-1&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Feedback Components &amp;lt;a class=&amp;quot;anchor&amp;quot; href=&amp;quot;#feedback-components&amp;quot; aria-hidden=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot;&amp;gt;#&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/h1&amp;gt;
